    proBonoResourcesPara: "Atlanta Volunteer Lawyers Foundation coordinates pro bono placement. The Atlanta Bar Association's pro bono program organizes legal clinics. The State Bar of Georgia's Pro Bono Project tracks participation statewide. Major Atlanta firms including King & Spalding, Alston & Bird, and Kilpatrick Townsend maintain structured programs. The Georgia Justice Project provides holistic legal services for people with criminal records.",
