    smallClaimsCourtPara: "California Small Claims Court handles claims up to $10,000 for individuals and $5,000 for businesses. San Diego Superior Court hears Small Claims at multiple courthouses. Filing fees run $30-$75. Attorneys are not permitted. Appeals go to Superior Court for trial de novo. The process runs 30-60 days from filing to hearing.",
