    commonDisputesPara: "The most common legal disputes in San Diego are immigration (asylum, adjustment of status, removal defense due to border proximity), family law (custody, divorce, military divorce under the Servicemembers Civil Relief Act), landlord-tenant matters (eviction defense, habitability), personal injury (auto accidents on I-5/I-8/I-15), and military-related legal matters.",
