  legalAidOptionsPara: "Legal Aid Society of Milwaukee provides free civil legal services for low-income Milwaukee County residents, covering housing, family law, and consumer protection. Legal Action of Wisconsin handles statewide impact litigation. LARS (Lawyers and Residents for a Stronger community) provides legal services on the North Side. The Marquette Volunteer Legal Clinic operates from Marquette Law School.",
